---
title: عدم دسترسی
sitemap: false
---

<header
  x-data
  class="absolute left-0 right-0 top-0 z-fixed flex h-16 shrink-0 grow-0 select-none items-center bg-surfaceContainer px-1 translucent"
>
  <button class="block cursor-pointer rounded-full p-3 text-[1.5rem] state-onSurface" @click="history.back()">
    {% alwatrIcon "arrow-forward-outline" %}
  </button>

  <div class="shrink grow text-ellipsis whitespace-nowrap px-1 text-start text-titleLarge text-onSurface">
    {{ title }}
  </div>
</header>

<main class="grow overflow-y-scroll px-2 pt-16">
  <section
    x-data
    x-cloak
    x-init="if($store.userProfile.data != null) location.href='/'"
    x-show="!$store.userProfile.data"
    class="mt-4 block cursor-pointer rounded-xl border border-outlineVariant border-opacity-50 p-10 text-center shadow-sm"
  >
    <div>
      <div class="text-[3rem]">{% alwatrIcon "lock-closed-outline", "inline-block" %}</div>
      <div class="mt-4 text-titleMedium">لطفا با رمز آدرس ارسال شده وارد شوید.</div>
      <a
        href="/"
        class="mx-auto mt-6 flex h-10 cursor-pointer select-none items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary px-2 transition-opacity elevation-0 state-onPrimary hover:elevation-1 active:elevation-0 aria-disabled:pointer-events-none aria-disabled:opacity-40"
      >
        {% alwatrIcon "home-outline", "text-[1.125rem]" %}
        <span class="px-2 text-labelLarge">بازگشت به صفحه اصلی</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
